OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTobacco firm calls for     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftougher rules on vapes     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The London-based tobacco company BAT   
OL,6, has called for "more stringent"        
OL,7, regulations on vaping, including a     
OL,8, licensing regime similar to alcohol and
OL,9, cigarettes.                            
OL,11,FIt also wants a ban on flavours which  
OL,12,F"uniquely" target children.            
OL,14,FThe government is already considering  
OL,15,Fnew regulations amid concerns that many
OL,16,Fyoung people are vaping.               
OL,18,FIt has promised legislation following a
OL,19,Fpublic consultation that is currently  
OL,20,Funderway.                              
